query:
UPDATE relatorios_livres rl
SET rl.gestorId = (
  SELECT g.id FROM gestores g 
  INNER JOIN users u ON g.userId = u.id 
  WHERE u.name LIKE '%F치bio%' OR u.name LIKE '%Fabio%'
  LIMIT 1
)
WHERE rl.gestorId NOT IN (SELECT id FROM gestores)
AND rl.lojaId IN (
  SELECT gl.lojaId FROM gestor_lojas gl 
  INNER JOIN gestores g ON gl.gestorId = g.id
  INNER JOIN users u ON g.userId = u.id
  WHERE u.name LIKE '%F치bio%' OR u.name LIKE '%Fabio%'
);
